ed</item></change><change n="meta.1955"><date>2009-03-20</date><respStmt><name>IDP</name></respStmt><item>Crosswalked to EpiDoc XML</item></change></revisionDesc></teiHeader><text><body><head lang="en"><date>240BC</date>
<placeName cert="high">Philadelphia</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Φίλων Ζήνωνι χαίρειν. εἰ ἔρρωσαι 

    <lb n="2"/>αὐτός τε καὶ οὓς θέλεις, εὖ ἂν ἔχοι· 

    <lb n="3"/>ἐρρώμην δὲ καὶ αὐτός. καλῶς ποι-

    <lb n="4"/>ήσεις ὑπὲρ ὧν Πτολεμαῖος 

    <lb n="5"/>ἀδελφὸς ἀναπέπλευκεν πρὸς 

    <lb n="ms,6"/>σέ 

    <lb n="6"/>ἐπιμελῶς διοικήσας, ἵνα τα-

    <lb n="7"/>χέως πρός με ἀναστρέφηι 

    <lb n="8"/>καὶ μὴ ἐπικωλύωμαι ἐὰν 

    <lb n="9"/>δέηι ἀναπλεῖν· συντόμως γὰρ 

    <lb n="10"/>δεῖ ἀποτρέχειν ἐντεῦθεν. 

    <lb n="11"/>ἔγραψα δέ σοι καὶ περὶ Ἑρμοκράτου 

    <lb n="12"/>πρότερον, διὰ τὸ ηἰσθῆσθαί σε σπεύ-

    <lb n="13"/>δονθ᾽ ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ καὶ αὐτὸς φα-

    <lb n="14"/>νερὸν αὐτῶι <choice><corr>πεποιηκέναι</corr><sic>πεποηκε<add place="supralinear">ναι</add></sic></choice>, καὶ σφό-

    <lb n="15"/>δρ᾽ οἴομαι ἡμερῶν ὀλίγων ἔξω 

    <lb n="16"/>αὐτὸν ἔσεσθαι. <choice><corr>ἐνωχλήθησαν</corr><sic>ηνωχληθησαν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="17"/>δ᾽ ὑπὲρ αὐτοῦ καὶ πλείους, 

    <lb n="18"/>ἐπετέλεσεν δὲ μάλιστα Κα-

    <lb n="19"/>φισοφῶν ὁ Φιλίππου τοῦ ἰατροῦ υἱός. 

    <lb n="20"/>καὶ τὴν ἀνάκρισιν τὴν ὑπὲρ 

    <lb n="21"/>αὐτοῦ γεγραμμένην, ἣ καὶ 

    <lb n="22"/>ἐπέλυεν αὐτὸν πάντων τῶν 

    <lb n="23"/>ἐπικληθέντων, εἶχεν ἤδη Δωσί-

    <lb n="24"/>θεος ὁ ὑπομνηματογράφος, ἵνα 

    <lb n="25"/>ὁ βασιλεὺς ἐπαναγνῶι πρὸ τοῦ 

    <lb n="26"/>ἀφεθῆναι <add place="supralinear">αὐτόν</add>, παρὰ τὸ ἔθος εἶναι οὕ-

    <lb n="27"/><add place="supralinear">τως γίνεσθαι</add>. τὰ δ᾽ ἄλλα συντόμως προσδέ-

    <lb n="28"/>χου καὶ αὐτοὺς ἡμᾶς· καὶ τῶν 

    <lb n="29"/>ἐν οἴκωι δέ, κἂν αὐτὸς θλίβηι 

    <lb n="30"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">δ</unclear>ιατηρήσ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ας</supplied> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear>μο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῦ</unclear> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τὸ</unclear>ν τόπ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ν τ<gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="31"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="line"/> 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="31"/>Ζήνωνι. 

    <lb n="31"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied>ἰς Φιλα-

    <lb n="32"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied>έλφειαν. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0240-03" notBefore="-0240-02" precision="low" type="textDate">ca. Febr. - März 240 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">55</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1955</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">55</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;1;55" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">C.Pap.Jud. I 127a</bibl></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations">TUAT, N.F. 3 (2006), VIII 3.1.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations">Orrieux, Les papyrus de Zenon (1983), S. 69</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Philadelphia</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.1955" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://wwwapp.cc.